title: Change our DAO vault reserve price from 1500 ETH to at least 3000 or more ETH.
body:
Since we are just starting out as a project and DAO, it would not be beneficial, especially for small(er) DAO investors that yet do not own whole lot of $FISH that the DAO vault get's it's reserve price met and sent on an auction where it might be sold to someone. We should raise our reserve price from 1500 ETH to at least double that value to stop this from happening, especially since we've added a lot of good NFT's to our vault lately. It's reserve price is way too low compared to what's in it and, like I said, we are just starting out and don't want our vault bought right now.
Link to our vault https://fractional.art/vaults/0x2604e9f68259e609e8744fb67cc410d50fc9aa0f
author: 0x323AcB6f6A930980Ad214900665805F678b8f813
